# Videoplayer resources and elements 

*Use AVKit Framework to create view-level services for media playback, complete with user controls and chapter navigation* : https://developer.apple.com/documentation/avkit

*AVPlayerViewController is an object that displays the video content from a player object along with system-supplied playback controls* : https://developer.apple.com/documentation/avkit/avplayerviewcontroller

*Use AVFoundation Framework to work with audiovisual assets, process audio, and configure system audio interactions* : https://developer.apple.com/documentation/avfoundation

*Use contentOverlayView to display a view between the video content and the playback controls* : https://developer.apple.com/documentation/avkit/avplayerviewcontroller/1615835-contentoverlayview

*An iOS video player based on AVFoundation* : https://iosexample.com/an-ios-video-player-base-on-avfoundation/

*Play local video with AVPlayerViewController and AVKit* : https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PilNQ2TkwGw


*Swift 4 - Embed and Play Video (AVPlayerViewController)* : https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RCVcqjjvZBM





